casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Sean Gardner SAXON.
No. D-2964.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 17, 2017.
Sean Gardner Saxon, of Arvada, Colorado, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
